// Checkbox
// Multi-select checkbox group where each option can be independently checked.

FUNCTION handleChange(value, checked)
  Adds or removes the value from the selected set.
  Calls onChange with the updated array of selected values.

---

FUNCTION Checkbox(props) -> ReactNode                                     EXPORT
  Renders a list of checkbox options with labels.
  Each checkbox maintains its own checked state based on the selected values array.
  Calls handleChange when any checkbox is toggled.
